main rm

Remove a package

USAGE:
    main rm [OPTIONS] <PACKAGE>

ARGUMENTS:
        <PACKAGE>
            Package name to remove

OPTIONS:
    -h, --help
            Show help message and exit.
    -V, --version
            Show version and exit.
        --completions <bash,zsh,fish>
            Generate shell completions.
    -y, --yes
            Don't ask for confirmation
